snippet.title: Let's Play Vlad Tepes Dracula pt1(b)
snippet.description: Hello ladies and gents, thank you for returning to my Let's Play of Vlad Tepes Dracula, a game i played as a kid and enjoyed it thoroughly. It's a game that's pretty under-the-radar as far as I know, so i thought i'd do a let's play and see what everyone else thought of it. Here's part 2 of part 1 XD but yes, after listening back on myself i realize the game can overshadow my voice slightly, so i'll be turning down the volume for the next parts. Hope you enjoy ;)
